article.linkText: Tennessee State wins 85-53 against Tennessee Tech
article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- — Christian Brown scored 14 points as Tennessee State beat Tennessee Tech 85-53 on Thursday night. Brown had five rebounds for the Tigers (10-9, 3-3 Ohio Valley Conference). Jaylen Jones was 4-of-8 shooting (4 for 6 from 3-point range) to add 14 points. EJ Bellinger was 5-of-8 shooting (3 for 6 from 3-point range) to finish with 13 points. Jayvis Harvey finished with 17 points, four assists and three steals for the Golden Eagles (7-12, 2-4). Tennessee Tech also got 13 points from Rodney Johnson Jr.. Josiah Davis also had 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
